# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
#
# NOTE: subdomain root routing (blog./app./client.husrihtlaefan.org -> their
# pages) does NOT live here — Pages ignores host-matched 200 rewrites (host
# sources only work for 3xx redirects, verified 2026-07-11). It's handled
# server-side by functions/_middleware.js instead, routed via _routes.json.
#
# The Fund Portal (fund.html) is reachable at the clean URL /fund via Cloudflare
# Pages' native clean-URL serving — no rewrite rule needed here (an explicit
# /fund -> /fund.html rewrite fights Pages' automatic /fund.html -> /fund 308 and
# causes a redirect loop).
